---
title: Orange & Cherry-Glazed Pork Steak with Mash & Almond Veggies
description: We’re bringing the sweet and juicy taste of a fruit orchid to your pork steak dinner with a rich orange and cherry
glaze. It adds those zesty sweet notes to brighten up this dish and leave you with a smile that only vibrant fruit can bring.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*Unfortunately, this
week's silverbeet was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with baby
spinach. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
